{"lemma":"فَحَماتِ","slug":"فَحَماتِ","root":"ف.ح.م","root_slug":"ف-ح-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ح-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n33157","n33162"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n33157","headword_ar":"فحّمهُ","root":"fHm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafoHiymN","text_ar":"تَفْحِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He blackened it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K,) namely, another's face, (S, A, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHom","text_ar":"فَحْم"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"charcoal"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.)       -A2-  See also the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":["S","A","Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n33162","headword_ar":"فَحْمَةٌ","root":"fHm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"n. un. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHomN","text_ar":"فَحْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. [Hence] one says of a black woman with a red"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ximaAr","text_ar":"خِمَار"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or muffler],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaA^an~ahaA","text_ar":"كَاَنَّهَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHomapN fiY raA^osihaA naArN","text_ar":"فَحْمَةٌ فِى رَاْسِهَا نَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"As though she were a piece of charcoal with fire upon its head"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  [And hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHomapu All~ayoli","text_ar":"فَحْمَةُ اللَّيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first part of the night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the blackness of the night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the most intense blackness of the night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the blackness of the first part of the night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the most intensely black part of the night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the part from the setting of the sun to"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the time of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the sleeping of mankind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) so called because of its heat [as well as its darkness]; for the first part of the night is hotter than its last part: (TA:) it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"peculiarly in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sayof","text_ar":"صَيْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"summer"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not in the winter:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHomapu AlEi$aA='i","text_ar":"فَحْمَةُ العِشَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the darkness of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"E$A'","text_ar":"عشاء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. of the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nightfall"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the intenseness of the blackness of the night,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its darkness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"which is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in its first part:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the time next after the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"E$A'","text_ar":"عشاء"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiHaAmN","text_ar":"فِحَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuHuwmN","text_ar":"فُحُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA:) or the latter of these may mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"darkness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though it were an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHuma","text_ar":"فَحُمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHomapu Als~aHari","text_ar":"فَحْمَةُ السَّحَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The time of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saHar","text_ar":"سَحَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"last part of the night"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHomapu bonu jumayorK","text_ar":"فَحْمَةُ بْنُ جُمَيْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is [a proper name of]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The middle of the night."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["K","Msb","TA","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}